INTRODUCTION
This is a text based poker client manly for bots to battle one and other.

Installation 1.0
inorder to compile the game on linux simply install build-essentials and run make
from a terminal while standing in this folder. To run enter the following command
 .\bin/poker.exe 

SECTION X.X
Any file belonging to the beating poker project should have one of the following headers

1, This header is primarily used for files where '#' initialises a comment.
#########################################
#                                       #
#       -----BEATING POKER------        #
#       - ~a Poole production~ -        #
#       ------------------------        #
#                                       #
#########################################
# filename:	"name"
# creator:	"creator"
# date: 	"date"
#
# "Enter description"
#########################################
#
# TODO:
#

2, This header is primarily used for .cc or .h files or any file where // initialises a comment.
//#########################################
//#                                       #
//#       -----BEATING POKER------        #
//#       - ~a Poole production~ -        #
//#       ------------------------        #
//#                                       #
//#########################################
//# filename:	"name"
//# creator:	"creator"
//# date: 		"date"
//#
//# "Enter description"
//#########################################
//#
//# TODO:
//#
